      <h1>Network Optimization</h1>
      <p>Faster, More Reliable Wi-Fi for Work, Play, and Everything In Between</p>
    </div>

    <section class="service-pricing">
      <h2>What's Included</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>Wi-Fi speed testing and dead zone analysis</li>
        <li>Router upgrades, placement, and optimization</li>
        <li>Wired vs wireless recommendations and installs</li>
        <li>Mesh system setup for large homes or multi-level buildings</li>
